Some of the things people usually tell me…
Q: how can you be in this shape at 54? 
A: discipline and sacrifice
Q: For you everything is easy with money…
A. It wasn’t easy at the beginning!
Q: What advice do you have for the younger generation? 
A. Keep fighting for your dreams and goals and NEVER give up! 
#gvlifestyle
